# Input

```md
*foo [*bar*](/url)*

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1 +1 @@
-*foo [*bar*](/url)*
+*foo [_bar_](/url)*
```

# Output

```md
*foo [_bar_](/url)*
```
